@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin((0.98 + (v1 + 0.03 * tmp + 0.22)))
    v0 = 0.56
    v2 = 0.09
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.exp(v0 + 0.71) / (v1 + 0.86 + v1 + 0.22)))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.73 / v0 + 0.37)) + ((v2 + 0.99 * v2 + 0.41) / (v0 + 0.37 / v2 + 0.59)))
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.exp(tmp + 0.65) - (v0 + 0.79 / v1 + 0.59)))
    data[tid] = v0
